data.description: Traditional spacious 3BR/2BA brick home on the edge of FBG. Split BR & open plan between the kitchen, living area, dining room & breakfast room. A lg sunroom w/ abundant windows & natural light is across the back of the home. The primary BR has a separate tub & shower & dual closets. Lots of custom cabinets & storage. Utility room w/ a sink & storage. There is RV storage, workshop & a lg storage building. Attached to the garage is a large metal carport + an underground shelter. Stove pipe for wood burning stove. 8/23 roof. No city taxes or STR permit required. $5000 allowance at closing.
